Features
--------
+ Don't match two search terms on the same user (e.g. 'git su j j' should select Johnny A and Johnny B)
+ Enable interactive/noninteractive mode for multi/ambiguous user selection
+ Add fully-qualified users to config when you switch to them (if they're not already in there)
Enable interactive adding of users
Enable pairs to be specified in the config as arrays
Make colors configurable because people like that stuff

Tasks
--------
+ Change "git-su" config namespace to "gitsu"
+ Fix URLs on acknowledgements page
Use a prerelease version (e.g. "1.2.3.pre") for Gem working version

Bugs
--------
+ group email address is the wrong way around!
+ typing `git su --add user otheruser` adds the first user and switches to the second

